{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RoRmj8vWRX2sKLQMB1Trqi","type":"tool_result","content":"<system-reminder>This memory is 22 days old. Memories are point-in-time observations, not live state — claims about code behavior or file:line citations may be outdated. Verify against current code before asserting as fact.</system-reminder>\n1\t---\n2\tname: Fix pre-existing test failures before running spec loops\n3\tdescription: Pre-existing test infra issues are invisible during iteration but block the final verify gate\n4\ttype: feedback\n5\t---\n6\t\n7\tFix pre-existing test failures before starting an autonomous spec loop. The loop's per-iteration verify (`pnpm test`) may pass if the failing tests are in unrelated files, but the final `./scripts/verify` gate will block.\n8\t\n9\t**Why:** Spec 400 loop ran 16 iterations successfully, each noting \"5 pre-existing test files failing with ECONNREFUSED\" in logs. Iteration 17 was the first to run full verify and blocked. The fix was trivial (5 test files using hardcoded `localhost:5432` instead of Unix socket fallback).\n10\t\n11\t**How to apply:** Before `./scripts/spec-loop.sh`, run `./scripts/verify` once. If it fails on pre-existing issues, fix them first. The loop can't distinguish its own failures from inherited ones.\n12\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"39eb5474-9f91-4902-88f7-7ddd830071a9","uuid":"9b8a1030-7497-4835-9313-25f886c88d55","timestamp":"2026-04-26T20:26:09.138Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/vscode/.claude/projects/-workspaces-rng-utopia/memory/feedback_fix_test_infra_before_loops.md","content":"---\nname: Fix pre-existing test failures before running spec loops\ndescription: Pre-existing test infra issues are invisible during iteration but block the final verify gate\ntype: feedback\n---\n\nFix pre-existing test failures before starting an autonomous spec loop. The loop's per-iteration verify (`pnpm test`) may pass if the failing tests are in unrelated files, but the final `./scripts/verify` gate will block.\n\n**Why:** Spec 400 loop ran 16 iterations successfully, each noting \"5 pre-existing test files failing with ECONNREFUSED\" in logs. Iteration 17 was the first to run full verify and blocked. The fix was trivial (5 test files using hardcoded `localhost:5432` instead of Unix socket fallback).\n\n**How to apply:** Before `./scripts/spec-loop.sh`, run `./scripts/verify` once. If it fails on pre-existing issues, fix them first. The loop can't distinguish its own failures from inherited ones.\n","numLines":12,"startLine":1,"totalLines":12}}}
